          "reviewBody": "This school is shitass and terribly managed when it comes to handling traffic. With each student arriving by car, it causes heavy traffic congestion and contributes significantly to pollution as well as their parents park in the front of the houses also. It would be much better for the environment and people living in this area if the school invested in buses. The traffic jams during drop-off and pick-up times are incredibly frustrating leads to traffic jams for approximately atleast 1-2 hours. Also some of the parents doesn't know how to drive or the basic traffic rules and parking sense. Try to solve it with the trustees or the head of the school.",
