            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Vivek high school is the best place for your child. The teachers are very kind and push you to do your best at everything. Have a lot of amazing memories with my friends here. Playing basketball and badminton with friends is just so memorable. Has alot of extracurricular activities like art, guitar, theatre, singing, dance, etc. This school also has a lot of different ways of entertainment like performance assemblies and founders with different themes every year!! All kids wait for founders all year. There are inter house competitions held as well. In the end I just want to say that I love it here and  wish to have more amazing memories 💗🎀",
